snippet.title: Sesh Gaan Noy Aaj | Mangal Deep | Bengali Movie Video Song | Md Aziz | Tapas Paul,Satabdi Roy

localized.description:
Bengali film song "Sesh Gaan Noy Aaj" from the movie Mangal Deep released in year 1989 starring Tapas Paul,Satabdi Roy,Ranjit Mullick,Anup Kumar. Bappi Lahiri scored the music in the film.

Song Name : Sesh Gaan Noy Aaj
Artist : Mohammed Aziz
Lyricist : Bhabesh Kundu
Music Director : Bappi Lahiri
Movie : Mangal Deep
Release : 1989
Director : Hiranath Chakraborty
Star Cast : Tapas Paul,Satabdi Roy,Ranjit Mullick,Anup Kumar
